{
  "stem": "22582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Gross Rosen for about-- I don't exactly remember how many days, but it was at least eight days and probably close to two weeks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they transported us to a new camp, and-- which was located in Wuestegiersdorf.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in Silesia, in German Silesia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It now belongs to Poland, I believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a new camp, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The camp was located in an old porcelain Fabrik, where they used to [? be ?] they used to make porcelain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was some Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, they started to bring people from Hungary in camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were in charge.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember, the Lagerfuhrer, the German, was-- Schwartz was his name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And actually they sent us again, first the last [? guy who ?] came in [? towards ?] work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you used go, and we do some work with the stones and with the-- and put in for the train something-- the wooden things for the train.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know how you call it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In any case, I was working there for awhile, for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, somehow we found out they needed people to work at the-- at the-- at the station, train station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember how I got there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed young people who knew how to work, because with Germans, in the wartime especially, very important was that the train should be roaring.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Train shouldn't be staying empty for a minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as soon as the train came in with something, it had to be unloaded.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you have to wait for another train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were looking for people who-- young people who would do the job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow I got in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were all young people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
